<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-870] add concurrent merge policy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-870</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Provide the ability to handle merges in one or more concurrent threads, i.e., concurrent with other IndexWriter operations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m factoring the code from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-847&quot; title=&quot;Factor merge policy out of IndexWriter&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-847&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
